Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toys
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.12,0:00:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被选中的人心中鼓起的奇迹的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的人会开出纯洁的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦有的人会开出毒花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大侦探时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争奇斗艳的两朵鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为侦探以及怪盗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 安利艾特 给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被退学了还在这里呆那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少大家一起对学院进行最后的告别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家向宿舍说 “谢谢了” 吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是被赶出来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没能成为侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milky Holmes解散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 夏洛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们总算是回老家结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来品尝胜利的美酒吧 小猫们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就是开瓶盖的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚森大人应该也会高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我没认真做的错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的话 这就是最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次要真正的将你们逼到绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:13.59,c,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的横滨大峡谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蒜拉面还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等 马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的汤面还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说很快就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板粘糊糊的 我的脚被...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 现在马上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边咋办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起就想完事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的汤面还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着下一则新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横滨警署发表公告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两周怪盗亚森所领导的怪盗帝国在横滨犯案已达26件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排骨 NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 咲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上的传言原来是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛在偏僻的店里打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很偏僻 但对我来说是很重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你 因为已经有新品种了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然听说是很偏僻的店 但这是哪啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏僻的拉面店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵退散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么偏僻的店肯定很多恶灵的 恶灵退散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沦落到在偏僻的地方做舞女 也不要去死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然比较偏僻 但是没有想跳舞 也没说要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.83,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:38.51,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说偏僻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有很多侦探在追捕怪盗帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到目前暂时还是素手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 亚森他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这两周每天都在搞事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:54.55,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要点啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初只是偷些珠宝和画而已 后来慢慢变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚终于偷了一个高层大厦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且因为那样别的怪盗也变多起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes侦探学院的大家好像因为追捕他们每天都很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚森又活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚森 绝对不会让你逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行人给我一边呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.73,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.81,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃霸王餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…额？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.22,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多少有多少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答是Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是G 你现在要想去吃牛肉火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 羊栖菜客饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛肉火锅你是喜欢加红生姜还是不加红生姜啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂妮娅 妮洛 原来你们在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请买我的诗集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 夏洛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没吃肉包了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 在拉面馆打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能我还真比较适合做这行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也试过做汉堡包房的工作 但是不是很适合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我很怕黑 不然会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在家庭餐厅做过 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你们点菜集中点嘛 等决定好了再叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说店里的人对我还是挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我还是想继续向上努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我分发过T-shirt 但是再也不想做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.95,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦都横滨也变了很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是怪盗 现在都可以叫怪都横滨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横滨的各位 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚森！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微让你们欣赏下余兴节目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes侦探学院的学生会长安利艾特·米斯特鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要破坏侦探学院的话 我们的工作就完成了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 横滨将不再是侦都而成为怪盗的天堂 怪都
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是横滨大树海的.. 是横滨大峡谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊着她的绳子将会每2小时一根根地断掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这城市还有相信正义的笨蛋的话就来救她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一个不剩的将你们抹杀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将横滨变成怪盗的天国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做那么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横滨要完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么办啊 安利艾特小姐被...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚森 不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么说 我们已经是普通人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能做啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G4一定会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能装扮成美丽的亚森大人只有美丽的我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢喜欢 托艾特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是搞不懂的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就算是亚森大人 万一从那里掉下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是抱着这样的心理准备 要将那些自称正义的家伙干掉的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以自身为诱饵 一定也是在测试我们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪盗帝国 逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的将杂兵全部干掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离怪都还差多少人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点来啊 Millky Holmes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉面还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上送到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记放鸡蛋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横滨由我们G4来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横滨大峡谷 NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快放开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快放开的话小衣告你妨碍公务逮捕你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么简单 对付警察的走狗们只要几秒钟就搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是充满无知者的节庆日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G4的明智小衣也就是这副惨样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 开始准备Party吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和侦都横滨说再见了~啾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一个安利艾特都救不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废柴警察！可恶可恶可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离这个小镇的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与安利艾特·米斯特鲁的命运完结还差两小时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两小时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天风很大 可能撑不了那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.89,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我差不多点 加油啊 废柴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.89,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了再来了！炒你鱿鱼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像月光一样 坚强 梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人的名叫安利艾特·米斯特鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 月亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再一次照亮黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 安利艾特能得救吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救 不能得救 得救…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 去救安利艾特！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我们的Toys…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经不是Holmes侦探学院的学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说有必要去救逼我们退学的那个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！妮洛你个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管再怎么落魄 也要自己成为自己所憧憬的那个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为自己所想要成为的那个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢 我们不是没能成为侦探嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么憧憬不也没能成功嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为中途放弃了的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们自己放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管退学了或是怎么了还是能成为侦探的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像梅利与凯特那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 最重要的人在危急时无视她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是成为侦探之前的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我最喜欢的大家变成那样...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错了 不该和你争执的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忽视了做人的重要道理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛 我不知什么时候忘记了 这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 再一次相信自己看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去救安利艾特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milky Holmes+鱼糕 出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点啊 才跑了10分钟而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 只有睡觉我才擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃东西很擅长 跑步就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去横滨大峡谷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上来 送你们去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳·朵阿拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在横滨大树海遇难那时夏洛你们救出来的那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的是 我把她们救出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后备箱也很宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:15:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快件送到了噗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索尼亚寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你封有我的Toys的一次性戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有和我同一系统的Toys夏洛克前辈的话应该你能用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索尼亚上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 索尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个看上去很有用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个噗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是克拉里斯公主寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚典礼上剩余的回赠品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没人来 横滨人到底都有没有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探到来了很多 那就是横滨的水平吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 警察都那样了也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有30分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都没人来了啦 把亚森大人放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹剧结束了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在时间到之前要是放下来的话怪盗帝国会被解散 她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去告诉亚森大人 已经没人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One Two Three
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们不算数...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪盗帝国！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换一张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边是同花的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开安利艾特小姐！听到了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪：扑克用语
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加 怎么可能同花 不就是猪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们的手段吗？拉比特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看错你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你们不会做抓人质这种事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的美学 丑陋的托艾特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开啊 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 夏洛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被亚森大人抛弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能做的只有这些了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 夏洛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 你个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼到绝境吧 更多一点 把Milky Holmes逼到绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑陋的我…丑陋…丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托艾特 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人 卑鄙小人 卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 就算这么做 没有Toys的你们是赢不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我输了的话 夏洛就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能救安利艾特的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们Milky Holmes的胜利 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀背打而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚森大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夏洛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的 都回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你忠实而又美丽的飞人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看Milky Holmes！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起飞 很美丽...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的乳头离起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特 得救了太好了 Toys…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打赌还是我的赢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 亚森！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把安利艾特藏哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天终于能将真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 在危机时刻爆发出潜力的比平时更强的你彻底击败了
